sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant User
    participant Surface as Surfaces
    participant Capture as Context Capture Layer
    participant Store as State + Timeline Store
    participant Memory as Memory Subsystem
    participant Resume as Resume
    participant Core as LLM Reasoning Core
    participant Policy as Interaction / Attention Policy
    participant UI as Extension UI

    User->>Surface: Works in editor
    Surface->>Capture: Active context signals
    Capture->>Capture: Normalize and redact
    Capture->>Store: Append WorkContextEvent
    Store->>Memory: Update working memory
    User->>Surface: Interruption happens
    Surface->>Capture: Last context signals
    Capture->>Store: Append gap marker
    User->>UI: Where was I?
    UI->>Resume: Request resume
    Resume->>Store: Read recent timeline
    Resume->>Memory: Read working memory
    Resume->>Core: Reconstruct state
    Core-->>Resume: Cited resume summary
    Resume->>Policy: Candidate surface
    Policy-->>UI: Propose resume
    UI-->>User: Show state and next steps
